# Redirect old query-parameter filter URLs to clean canonical paths.
# Bank-specific landing-page redirects have separate /banks/<slug>/ pages now,
# and the homepage canonicalizes filtered states to / via the canonical meta
# tag in index.html, so /?banks=...&rests=... URLs are kept as-is.

# 404 fallback: any path that doesn't match a real file falls through to
# 404.html with HTTP 404. Cloudflare Pages serves 404.html by default for
# missing routes, but stating it explicitly survives wrangler-dev and any
# future routing changes. Order matters — this MUST stay last.
/*  /404.html  404
